{"tid":395392,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"（求救）滅蟻方法","createTime":"2017-09-10T17:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T03:52:56.000Z","uid":118158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3ac3dc3f5a699c3f87e010c1d895cd6c5c974750","tid":395392,"uid":118158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T17:39:46.000Z","msg":"車泊露天，之前大風之後洗車發現有蟻窩係門檻位殺蟲水噴過一次以為安樂晒<br />\n<br />\n點知早幾日洗車係車頭乘客位防水膠邊又發現一個，但唔敢拆開條防水膠邊睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見佢地出出入入<br />\n<br />\n有無咩方法可以令佢地冚家剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ac06923cd5c6f65d211b83ee5a05857f35fa15","tid":395392,"uid":17759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T17:41:53.000Z","msg":"我都試過 用藥餌<br />\n<br />\n用過一排 見到佢地死鳩哂 諗住以為無事<br />\n<br />\n點知過一排又出現返 我拎水喉係咁沖 沖哂成架車 連個車底都噴 總知見到有蟻出現嘅地方係咁沖 附近都沖埋 <br />\n<br />\n跟住而家都未過d蟻出現返 成個禮拜了 我諗無事掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec5e4f9dad9888f39ed30e67c5c344d525287b28","tid":395392,"uid":17759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T17:44:23.000Z","msg":"如果你放左藥餌 見到佢地都唔好殺佢地住 <br />\n<br />\n可能佢地擺緊d餌入蟻窩食 <br />\n<br />\n過一排先洗車 .<br />\n<br />\n應該會食死哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/11/014417_a5d67a880a5cea3fe597e079be9aa43f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F11%2F014417_a5d67a880a5cea3fe597e079be9aa43f.jpg&h=667248ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用過呢隻"},{"pid":"b9c4336f65071896ba229a92fd7a9d1064